                                   E-MAIL
                         Link to Albuquerque E-mail
    When providing information to the Albuquerque Division of the FBI via
     e-mail, please include your name, telephone number, and address, if
               possible, in the event we need to contact you.
   Although the e-mail we receive is reviewed, the FBI does not guarantee
   a response to all messages. Do not include any attachments when sending
               us e-mail since all systems are not compatible.
      Please contact your local FBI office by telephone with questions
       regarding employment, the Freedom of Information Act, or other
                   questions requiring a direct response.
